<ss:Data ss:Type="String">iShares Physical Gold ETC</ss:Data>
</ss:Cell>
</ss:Row>
<ss:Row/>
<ss:Row ss:Height="50">
<ss:Cell ss:MergeAcross="11" ss:StyleID="wraptext">
<ss:Data ss:Type="String">The iShares Physical Gold ETC only accepts gold that meets The London Bullion Market Association (LBMA) Good Delivery rules. In-line with these rules, the bars also aim to comply with LBMA’s Responsible Sourcing Programme ensuring that 100% of the gold bullion backing our ETC is responsibly sourced (as at 31 March 2022). iShares will continue to work with our gold custodian to only allocate gold mined post-2012 to the ETC. For further details on responsible sourcing please see the iShares Responsible Sourcing Guide here and the LBMA website : www.lbma.org.uk/guidance-documents. Securities issued under the iShares Physical Gold ETC Series are compliant with Shariah investment principles.</ss:Data>
</ss:Cell>
</ss:Row>
<ss:Row/>
